---
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">Why pwnkit</h2>
      <p class="text-ash text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">No YAML. No subscriptions. No false positives shipped.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-crimson/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 mb-5 text-crimson">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-base mb-3">Zero config</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-smoke leading-relaxed">No YAML. No Python. Just <code class="text-white/60 bg-white/5 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">npx pwnkit-cli</code> and you're running.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-crimson/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 mb-5 text-crimson">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-base mb-3">Blind verification</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-smoke leading-relaxed">Every finding is independently re-exploited. Can't reproduce it? Killed as a false positive.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-crimson/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 mb-5 text-crimson">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-base mb-3">Bring your own AI</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-smoke leading-relaxed">Your API key, or use Claude Code CLI / Codex CLI with your subscription. Any model, any provider.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
